            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onions are cooking, dissolve 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1] </span><strong>Knorr</strong> <strong>vegetable stock cube </strong>and<strong> </strong>the<strong> tomato paste</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
