    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>torn jackfruit</strong>, <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 4-5 min or until browned</p><p>Meanwhile, tear (or crumble!) the <strong>vegan cheese </strong>into small pieces</p>",
